<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" id="CITEREFWO2008037004"><a href="http://v3.espacenet.com/textdoc?DB=EPODOC&amp;IDX=WO2008037004" class="external text" title="http://v3.espacenet.com/textdoc?DB=EPODOC&amp;IDX=WO2008037004" rel="nofollow">WO&#160;patent&#160;application&#160;2008037004</a>, <i>"An energy storage device and method of use"</i>, published 2008-04-03</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Apatent&amp;rft.applnumber=2008037004&amp;rft.cc=WO&amp;rft.title=An+energy+storage+device+and+method+of+use&amp;rft.inventor=Kwok%2C+James&amp;rft.appldate=2007-09-25&amp;rft.pubdate=2008-04-03&amp;rft.prioritydate=2006-09-25"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
